svg.text: The Pocket Learner System was created by parents
of a child who had learning difficultes, due to this many
other parents/guardians were able to use the system
to help their children learn. I was given the task of designing
a app for their current system.
To create the design for the app I used Adobe Illustrator.
The font used was Airfly DEMO.
This was my first attempt of designing a app.
